{"tid":574863,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女人究竟諗乜","createTime":"2018-02-27T18:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T00:23:06.000Z","uid":43873,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5bbb1793312c5728c4dd6af562774cb3d92d1dfe","tid":574863,"uid":43873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T18:22:05.000Z","msg":"長話短說 上星期頭同女朋友分左手<br />\n我叫佢block左我 佢話唔得 想繼續同我做朋友 繼續同我講心事講早晨晚安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想好似未一齊之前咁樣既關係<br />\n又話冇唔愛我 只係因為我地之間既一件事 佢過唔到自己 搞到要分開(係我自己衰仔做錯既)<br />\n我自己就自問做唔到朋友 有同佢講 佢話明白 然後繼續當我朋友咁<br />\n之後呢半個星期 試過好冷酷 又試過有關心佢 佢都會對我不瞅不睬<br />\n唉頂你咁點解又話要做翻朋友咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n究竟女人諗乜 利申冇帽 但係佢太人前人後搞到我諗唔明"},{"pid":"f93d6c2104876e03c40632d12dfb9493f2b8bcae","tid":574863,"uid":138138,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T18:23:13.000Z","msg":"真係幾長話短說"},{"pid":"62f449e5ac6b50b970f7dc6261df4f963ae36691","tid":574863,"uid":110112,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T18:51:59.000Z","msg":"佢未玩夠<br />\n想轉你做兵<br />\n一邊拖住你 <br />\n一邊攞正牌話自己單身等仔溝"},{"pid":"6e0eccd81641290325ba871a592d3c9f21da535a","tid":574863,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T18:53:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf4a0d65f27cf11c031c21c8b856277d3f28fc10","tid":574863,"uid":43873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f93d6c2104876e03c40632d12dfb9493f2b8bcae","tid":574863,"uid":138138,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T18:23:13.000Z","msg":"真係幾長話短說"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T20:09:47.000Z","msg":"周圍都見到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"072febf7a78c2e69021e8804b22b537f86f80856","tid":574863,"uid":43873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62f449e5ac6b50b970f7dc6261df4f963ae36691","tid":574863,"uid":110112,"lik